" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120200952l8B0diTRsP7vfkYo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120200956VwxBM9Tgk1GjJW08.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201010fJw9yLCVUmepMhn5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201015We9C0oc6XlKJGA7V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201019fHUWLIwpVdGhyZS3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201032dQ6GLTWYnquyikCU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202010449zJxhR4LjfB5ON0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201045Xr1Liwjt2dIBu3Fh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202012055fKjQcRYp9IbuXeG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201659KkCUhH5Tft8NIDLZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012020171159Oh6E3yztW2eav4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201712GRAzLBCJoN7nHQph.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202013476YPXdmr0bGIC1ASJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201404UzBMvW59sPDFN1KE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201711h6yaQORgGKqvESFi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201714580vPwluhDmKYzCO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201713pQUHgX1acNRVzoih.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201715PLbpy5uYA8gnTl4k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120201430xoLca23lfiQv7Bhz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2019/paris/jil-sander/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jil Sander 2019 秋冬男装：</a></strong></p><p>这是&nbsp;Lucie Meier&nbsp;和&nbsp;Luke Meier 夫妻从 2017 年 4 月起担任 Jil Sander 创意总监以来的第一场男装秀。秀场选在了所罗门罗斯柴尔德公馆（Hôtel Salomon de Rothschild）。</p><p>整个系列看上去非常干净，令人回想起创始人 Jil Sander 初创该品牌时的风格：90 年代极简主义，对于面料和长短比例的深入研究和实验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202249euUoc4asvdPRFTnm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202248F7TCfOLjcxt0ParB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202022484fkT9oXEnp7tOw2I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202248YlQMKTv6amCNHiZz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202249X6CriW3lRqf5nkKj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202250zvipHj6J5OTqCx3s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202022509hjPqyNVwQt7H25Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202248o05McuhmtSHGTgWN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202250WzmRJhTVKnPMoQ6x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202250k8OteLhJS7dBljXH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202251e81fdTn93kSNxWmY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202022544HR2bDQGLtu8yvBc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202022558p9y7coQtvzuhKxe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202022559ycaKQ1EzMi6dlJk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202255qQfus73UgOTCDtHx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202255Cfo4hxEwIGLcWdga.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202256C0Ya9TPMjBNRvGyt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202256KN1e9zc3SXsZgD8I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202256VzQdWxORTiILSClr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202257RcT6UPIpLWD5M2oE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202022578WVEyhzGOcuFfar5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120202257uV3pb9xe7agF2tHB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/fall-2019-menswear/raf-simons\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raf Simons 2019 秋冬男装：</a></strong></p><p>这是 Raf Simons 离开 Calvin Klein 不到一个月以来第一次出现在公众面前。他表示这个系列在去年圣诞节之前就已经完成了，没有受到离职事件及随之而来的争议的影响。“我不想消极看待（时尚业）。我想做一些抽象、美丽、优雅、成熟、令人自豪的东西，但不能失去这个品牌所代表的先锋感：年轻一代、暗黑电影”。<a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/fall-2019-menswear/raf-simons\" rel=\"nofollow\">他对 <em>Vogue</em> 说</a>。</p><p>该系列中最突出的是肩线夸张、颜色饱和度高的超长大衣（maxi coats）。此外，不少模特都穿着一条印有“Burning down the house”标语的白色棉质长裤。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202043489BjMhUzlAv5FaOK0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204343cRlykbNOGiMPmnDw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204346Axhi7d95rfnuOSGV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204355Hi12VYIk7Xc4zGsF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204351DAfULoY0gn3OG9Pu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204357AX9VLaNigZv32shH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202044071Udaq3k2YjWpz64o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204416eoCyw1HxAGFd2nEM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204416EYrhuPVpRbQiwmH1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202044174SlaXfcGdT2jLowI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204418nxRCTLBUAgiEre8d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204421cB4ykGe90RFDoUQY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204422SDJ7BrIgQGkw8Xnq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204424kIv0E4GwjpXB8LHW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204427ZsvL5zh3HRIBtrSC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204432Du5NGsmPwWjeFxz2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204436DpHvILeuEmNZr8fB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204442uy7t5o2pcqUDIY0h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204443wSupFAqWiZco50If.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012020444415zMdmt4W2uw7bLT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204453z6qmKbEjFhtOQZ34.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204454nsMYtLJ83j5afob6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202044564TwPAneYCdDBH1Rq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120204457lxVLmAuDjPq1U5GN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/fall-2019-menswear/hermes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hermès 2019 秋冬男装：</a></strong><br></p><p>秀场选在了法国国家家具管理局（Mobilier National），随处可见美得令人屏息的摄政时期、执政内阁时期以及路易十一式的家具。而 Vogue 时装评论人&nbsp;Luke Leitch 则抱怨嘉宾们都坐在了看上去像从宜家买的椅子上。</p><p>至于服装，较上一季变化不大，总得来说有些中规中矩。Véronique Nichanian 这次只是把夹克和外套做得长了一点。萝卜型皮裤的长度看上去有些尴尬——需要小心选择搭配的袜子和鞋 。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012021210227JnvmEukRwsXdtK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212103iUfzSVHnyluO0L9o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012021210448uaSwvZ3nF0DofW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212104ofsCnelPS2ZQ4KD7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202121064i30oslVQ7vkmh2X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212110QJeFDEGo4UzYVnC9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212109no87VGlKZUquILx0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212110WcEOTeIdkzhns8aP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202121123kN7jxI0pEH5RD8d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212112puvLSRDMVlIgbXj7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212115BQ9Ita3M8eNhoFLb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212116idQbmzewqra31Tp4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212119sFUBIloKNhjwiOmR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212118NAqQlFYn5DtaxSEd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212120UQBAqYvgS8nwG9NW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212121Ys2H6IgOL5amXTRi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212125XjG8Esl9BH2zbPOI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120212125KCXP14FfJZB9kabo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2019/paris/thom-browne/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thom Browne 2019 秋冬男装：</a></strong></p><p>Thom Brown 的秀场设在巴黎国立高等美术学院（Ecole nationale supérieure des Beaux-arts de Paris）。为了强调可持续的主题，整个秀场（包括嘉宾座椅）都被蒙上了气泡膜，模特们的面部也盖上了一层保鲜膜——尽管看上去一点也不环保。<a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2019/paris/thom-browne/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thom Browne 对<em> WWD</em> 解释说</a>，“我们使用的气泡膜是运输衣服时使用的外包装，所以可以说秀场装饰基本都用物流废料解决了。”<br></p><p>从服装来说，整个系列在延续性别模糊概念的同时也展示了该品牌一贯的优势：复杂工艺和精湛的男士套装剪裁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222923XcztaYDKUE1luSWw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222711Sa80wH5zXFQkTBPj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222925V8YbfdtFm0uCXzL6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222926x0qQaRd5MkY2GSsE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222928ZNj5Tbp9AcuFh1f0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202229296WimEDRFnZapoQ04.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222930pfUivQNnt7WyAeqO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222931atLsEWxJwfM5RAG0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202229328WvDd9jMFSYRVrys.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222934VG80oKQzRMCyABqU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901202229359VGO1kyEJMfXWwbm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222936QURs1VD3JuLIm6PF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222937OLZuaYw3xEgRlp2T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222939m9fCjJMl7UvFXn36.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222941KpWeAjNbu8rfimDQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222941J8TdA0uUI7faeXgH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222943un52gsLvHRkiXhlE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222943A71wYhUWSVFXxrGb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120222954tGPc5x3Hil9zNAnf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120223221WZp6FltsYr4qdyIn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>巴黎时装周上的中国设计师品牌：</strong></p><p>我们在 1 月 16 日的浮华日报中介绍了 Sankuanz（上官喆）。在随后的几天中，台湾设计师江奕勋的 Angus Chiang 和孙小峰的 Sean Suen 也展示了新系列。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2019/paris/angus-chiang/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Angus Chiang 2019 秋冬男装：</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120215909sndDFOKwkGh0C5Eu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120215657Vd7E4ukYlTH6Ua0j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190120215701IhCRB8ucjGHEks2Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: